INSERT INTO scanned_ballots (
            id,
            server_id,
            client_id,
            machine_id,
            election_id,
            cast_vote_record,
            created_at
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
        ON CONFLICT (client_id, machine_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            server_id = $2,
            election_id = $5,
            cast_vote_record = $6,
            created_at = $7
